@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ipksfr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.43 / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.73) + (v0 + 0.52 * v1 + 0.76)))
    v1 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.38) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.44)) + 0.05)
    tmp = (0.57 + wp.exp((tmp + 0.44 + v0 + 0.93)))
    data[tid] = v0
